			<munit-tools:assert doc:name="Assert payload" doc:id="b410481e-19ec-4b87-8a5b-48e27d16d0dd" message="The payload does not match">
				<munit-tools:that ><![CDATA[#[%dw 2.0
import cicdapiexampleFlowtest::assert_expression_payload
---
